<P>With Some Good HOPES of <HI>Better Things</HI> to be yet seen in the AMERICAN World.</P>
<P>In a SERMON, To the GENERAL ASSEMBLY of the <HI>Massachusett</HI>-Province in NEW-ENGLAND. 3 <HI>d.</HI> 9 <HI>m.</HI> 1709.</P>
