<P>For men to <HI>Employ</HI> others, and not <HI>Reward</HI> them according to <HI>Contract</HI>; [A Crime, not at all the less, because the <HI>Minister</HI> is not seldom the <HI>Sufferer</HI> from it!] Or, to with-hold from the <HI>Labourer</HI> his <HI>Wages,</HI> till his <HI>Cry</HI> reach up to Heaven; or break their Faith with their <HI>Creditors,</HI> and keep them out o<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> their Dues! <HI>Tis an Abomination!</HI></P>
