<P><Q>So use them, as to preserve Christs Right and Interes<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> in them. Those that k<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ep their <HI>Negro's</HI> and Slaves, from Hearing of Gods Word, and from becoming Christians, because, they shall then lose part of their Ser|vice, do openly profess Rebellion a|gainst
